Specifically, when you are

  * **Using the Chainstack Console** , we process your name, surname, email address (your account identifier), organization name, IP address, all HTTP headers (most importantly User-Agent), cookies;
  * **Using the Chainstack Blockchain infrastructure** , we process nodes’ token stored in Chainstack Vault, IP address and HTTP headers, request body, API token in Chainstack Vault.
